      "notes": "Site lists volumes under /volumes/volume-{N}. Each volume page lists articles each as div.sqs-block-content containing title (h4.sqs-html-content or div.sqs-text-block-container) and a direct PDF link. No per-article detail page. Navigation uses simple pattern."
